reviewText: This man is an incredible artist on the Spanish flamingo guitar. This DVD is one of his greatest but VERY HARD to find as it is only sold at his concerts and by the public broadcast channels. It was a bit pricey at 50.00 but the fact that you cant find it very often and that the public broadcast channels want 60.00 to 100.00 for it, it was a bargain. I love every second of it.
This man and his band - love them!!!!
